BERNICE FEIN ON FRIDAY

20
00:00:39,081 --> 00:00:41,834
AND I CAN'T EVEN FIT
INTO MY LUCKY JEANS.

21
00:00:41,917 --> 00:00:43,043
"DUMP THE LUMPS"
BERNICE FEIN?

22
00:00:43,126 --> 00:00:44,169
AS IN THE AGENT FROM HELL?

23
00:00:44,795 --> 00:00:45,879
(SIGHS) IF SHE'S SATAN,

24
00:00:45,963 --> 00:00:49,174
THEN THAT EXPLAINS WHY
SHE'S THE BEST AGENT IN TOWN.

25
00:00:49,258 --> 00:00:51,802
SHE CALLED BECAUSE SHE SAW ME
IN THE KEVIN SMITH MOVIE,

26
00:00:51,885 --> 00:00:54,763
WANTS TO AUDITION ME AGAIN.
(GRUNT OF EFFORT)

27
00:00:54,847 --> 00:00:56,849
CRISIS DOWN HERE!

28
00:00:56,932 --> 00:00:58,016
LOOK AROUND YOU.

29
00:00:58,100 --> 00:01:00,811
"CRISIS" IS ACTUALLY
AN EPIDEMIC.

30
00:01:00,894 --> 00:01:02,229
MY THIGHS ARE AN EPIDEMIC.

31
00:01:02,312 --> 00:01:04,481
AND THEY'RE TAKING OVER
THE WORLD.

32
00:01:04,565 --> 00:01:06,984
WE ARE GOING TO TAKE CONTROL.

33
00:01:07,067 --> 00:01:09,736
I AM GOING TO TAKE CONTROL.

