CALL FOR DESPERATE PURGING.

250
00:10:49,107 --> 00:10:49,983
MANNY;
IT'S NOT CALLED PURGING,

251
00:10:50,067 --> 00:10:51,985
IT'S CALLED BULIMIA.

252
00:10:52,069 --> 00:10:53,820
