THAT YOU'RE UNDISCIPLINED.

332
00:15:24,341 --> 00:15:26,176
THE AGENT'S GOING TO SEE
THAT I HAVE ENERGY

333
00:15:26,260 --> 00:15:26,969
AND ROSY CHEEKS,

334
00:15:27,052 --> 00:15:28,470
AND THAT I DON'T
HAVE PUKE BREATH.

335
00:15:28,554 --> 00:15:30,430
THIS IS SO
"TYPICAL MANNY".

336
00:15:30,514 --> 00:15:31,682
GIVE UP WHEN THE GOING
GETS TOUGH.

337
00:15:31,765 --> 00:15:33,350
IT'S ONE SLICE OF PIZZA,
EM!

338
00:15:33,433 --> 00:15:35,978
IT'S FAT AND STARCH
AND GREASE.

339
00:15:36,061 --> 00:15:37,980
