402
00:19:33,423 --> 00:19:36,718
AND THESE DISMEMBERED
MODELS ARE DISTURBING.

403
00:19:36,802 --> 00:19:38,011
IT'S INSPIRATION.

404
00:19:38,095 --> 00:19:39,513
FOR WHEN I WANT TO LOSE
A POUND.

405
00:19:39,596 --> 00:19:42,391
OKAY, BUT YOU'VE LOST,
LIKE, SEVEN.

406
00:19:42,474 --> 00:19:44,601
