430
00:20:44,036 --> 00:20:45,537
EMMA:
ARE YOU GUYS GONNA FINALLY
STOP CALLING EACH OTHER

431
00:20:45,621 --> 00:20:46,496
BY YOUR HIGH SCHOOL
NICKNAMES?

432
00:20:46,580 --> 00:20:47,331
MANNY:
(CHUCKLES)

433
00:20:47,414 --> 00:20:49,166
NOT A BAD IDEA,
BUT NO.

434
00:20:49,249 --> 00:20:50,459
UH, AS YOU ALL KNOW,

435
00:20:50,542 --> 00:20:52,127
I STILL HAVE
A MOTORCYCLE FUND.

436
00:20:52,211 --> 00:20:53,045
WHICH I WOULD LIKE TO USE

437
00:20:53,128 --> 00:20:55,214
NOT TO BUY
ANOTHER MOTORCYCLE WITH,

438
00:20:55,297 --> 00:20:56,632
BUT TO TAKE US ALL

439
00:20:56,715 --> 00:20:59,176
TO THE SHOPPING CAPITAL
OF THE WORLD -

440
00:20:59,259 --> 00:21:00,385
NEW YORK CITY.

441
00:21:00,469 --> 00:21:02,137
NEW YORK?
ARE YOU SURE?

442
00:21:02,221 --> 00:21:03,514
I'VE DONE ALL THE BORING,
PRACTICAL MATH

443
00:21:03,597 --> 00:21:04,306
AND WE'RE GOING, BABY.

444
00:21:04,389 --> 00:21:05,015
SPIKE:
ALL RIGHT!

445
00:21:05,098 --> 00:21:06,767
WAIT.
WHO'S INCLUDED IN "WE"?

446
00:21:06,850 --> 00:21:08,769
WELL UM, YOU ARE PART
OF THE NELSON-SIMPSON CLAN,

447
00:21:08,852 --> 00:21:09,895
ARE YOU NOT?

448
00:21:09,978 --> 00:21:11,688
I LOVE YOU!
I LOVE YOU GUYS!

449
00:21:11,772 --> 00:21:13,857
HOW MANY EMPTY SUITCASES
CAN I BRING?

450
00:21:13,941 --> 00:21:14,816
(JOKINGLY CAUTIONS MANNY)
HEY, WHOA! HEY.

451
00:21:14,900 --> 00:21:17,152
EMMA:
OKAY, THIS IS-
THIS IS BEYOND ANYTHING.

452
00:21:17,236 --> 00:21:18,570
IT ACTUALLY MIGHT BE ONE
OF THOSE MOMENTS.

453
00:21:18,654 --> 00:21:19,446
SO I'M GONNA
GET THE CAMERA.

454
00:21:19,530 --> 00:21:21,031
SIMPSON:
OH YEAH! CHEERS GUYS!

455
00:21:21,114 --> 00:21:22,282
SPIKE:
CHEERS!

456
00:21:22,366 --> 00:21:23,325
MANNY:
CHEERS!

457
00:21:23,408 --> 00:21:25,327
SIMPSON:
WOO HOO!

458
00:21:27,412 --> 00:21:29,248
(TOILET FLUSHES)

